\[
\textrm{RHS } = \frac{3 pqr }{abc }
\]
\[
= \frac{3 (ad )(bd )(cd )}{abc }
\]
\[
= 3d ^3
\]"
  }, {
    "id": "s5",
    "n_params": 0,
    "step_txt": "
